Full build order cho BACKEND cluster:
Container image — Dockerfile sandbox (read-only OS, tmpfs, non-root user, network=none)
Warm Pool bootstrapper — docker run -d pre-warm khi server start, lưu container ID list
Pool Manager — data structure quản lý IDLE/BUSY state của từng container
Virgin Reset — pkill -9 -u sandbox_user + rm -rf /workspace/*, benchmark dưới 50ms
Health Monitor — ping TCP mỗi 5s, detect DEAD → kill → spawn replacement
Job Dispatcher — pick IDLE container, assign job, đánh dấu BUSY
Job Queue (Redis) — buffer khi pool full BUSY, FIFO + 30s timeout
Execution worker_thread — push code qua docker exec stdin, stream stdout/stderr từng dòng

Protocol Handler — parse custom packet [LEN][TYPE][PAYLOAD], route RUN → Dispatcher, PING → PONG
TCP Worker Server — net.createServer port, wire toàn bộ pipeline
Heartbeat Server :4000 — gửi hearbeat lên middleware
Integration test — gửi RUN packet end-to-end, verify stream output + reset cycle 